obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (34626)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title, application and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_21_28_00002_196520_1517807319565&sectionId=34626&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_21_28_00002_196520_1517807319565
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Warehousing`
  line `Corporations (Supplementary) Act, 1965.`
  line
  line `(2) It shall apply to the State specified in the Schedule:`
  line
  line `Provided that the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, add the name`
  line `of any other State to the Schedule in respect whereof resolutions have been passed by the Legislatures`
  line `of those States adopting this Act under clause (1) of article 252 of the Constitution in respect of the`
  line `storage of commodities other than those covered by the Warehousing Corporations`
  line `Act, 1962 (58 of 1962), and on the issue of any such notification the States so added shall be deem to`
  line `be States specified in the Schedule within the meaning of this sub-section.`
  line
  line `(3) It shall come into force on such date^1 , as the Central Government may, by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, appoint.`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. 27th November, 1965, vide notification No. G.S.R. 1713, dated 17th, Nevember, 1965, see Gazette of India, Part II,`
  line `sec. 3(i).`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (34627)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Application of the Act with respect to notified commodities.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_21_28_00002_196520_1517807319565&sectionId=34627&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_21_28_00002_196520_1517807319565
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `The Warehousing Corporations`
  line `Act, 1962 (58 of 1962), shall, in its application to the States for the time being specified in the`
  line `Schedule, have effect as if in clause (e) of section 2 of that Act the words and figures "being a`
  line `commodity with respect to which Parliament has power to make laws by virtue of entry 33 in List III`
  line `in the Seventh Schedule to Constitution" had been omitted.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
